  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1397000/extras/aa76fb9388f5059bc44788a619e78f83.avif?t=1668931139\" width=600 height=256 /></span><br>Zodiac DX is a side-scrolling action game, based on the Zodiac comic by A.Young. Play as three everyday students who depart Earth on an adventure that spans the cosmos!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1397000/extras/bac85223d105c221033119d88976fad6.avif?t=1668931139\" width=600 height=286 /></span><br>\t● 3 playable characters<br><br>\t● Tuned-up levels with Maniac challenge option<br><br>\t● Special boss rush and card game modes<br><br>\t● All-original graphics and soundtrack<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1397000/extras/3fa28a61133c799366188a22e6393386.poster.avif?t=1668931139\" width=600 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1397000/extras/3fa28a61133c799366188a22e6393386.webm?t=1668931139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1397000/extras/3fa28a61133c799366188a22e6393386.mp4?t=1668931139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>CONTROLS</strong><br><br>Gamepads are supported!<br>Keyboard: 🆉 🆇 🅲 🆅 ↑ ↓ ← → ESC<br><br><strong>STYLE</strong><br><br>Foxy Boxy games are developed to express the 1985-1992 era of video games",
